Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Carter steals rivals' thunder
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043w1b9
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 3 Feb 1980
President Carter's annual speech turns into a 'state of the world' triumph. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less